  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This clinical trial is designed to provide additional information on the safety and
      tolerability of vildagliptin (50 mg once daily (qd)) when used in patients with type 2
      diabetes mellitus (T2DM) and moderate or severe renal insufficiency.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
